Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.88,0:01:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.00,0:01:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙,那是人類第2個故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.24,0:01:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當地球無法負荷增加過多人口時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.32,0:01:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們在宇宙製造新的大地與城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是宇宙殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.88,0:02:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從第一個大型殖民地可供4千萬人生活時候起,\N宇宙世紀就開啟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一話 前奏曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這各巨大圓桶的自轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.44,0:02:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使內側牆壁的大地,產生人工重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.28,0:02:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3個具大鏡子,將陽光收到殖民地內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製造出森林與湖泊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.07,0:02:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏,氣象也是人工控制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.07,0:02:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣具大的建築物\N是在強化宇宙服與
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.17,0:02:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作業用機器人開發後才得以建設出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.93,0:02:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而這個作業用機器人,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還發展成戰鬥用機器人MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.64,0:03:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS是宇宙世紀產生的終極機動武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.95,0:03:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於米諾夫基粒子的被發現使雷達無用武之地的這個時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.59,0:03:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可進行格鬥戰的MS,成了最強的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.46,0:03:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後在知道那戰鬥能力\N足可與宇宙巡洋艦匹敵之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.96,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們開始燃起戰爭的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.79,0:03:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.55,0:03:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開發最初的量產MS薩克\N的宇宙殖民地國家SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.41,0:03:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自稱吉翁公國 對地球連邦宣佈獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代於是進入將地球與宇宙一分為二的混亂時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.47,0:03:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化悲傷為力量\N站起來吧,國民們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘記我們吉翁國公民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.19,0:04:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是被神選上的子民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有優良的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能拯救人類\N吉翁萬歲！ 吉翁萬歲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.62,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁萬歲！ 吉翁萬歲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地墜落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了彰顯薩克威力的這個計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.74,0:04:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬間就奪走數千萬人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅·雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.61,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶然間坐上聯邦軍\N最新銳MS高達的這位少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.62,0:04:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在多次作戰中,成長成無敵的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣的啊,是這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害，能量是通常的5倍以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.72,0:05:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被稱為白色MS的高達\N戰鬥力果然驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.79,0:05:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅覺醒成新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.75,0:05:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代稱這是人類的革新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七年後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人類的革新並沒有全部達成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類又開始再度戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.88,0:05:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[泰坦斯要塞.格林普斯2]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.68,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由軍人精英組成,以管理地球本身為目標的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.31,0:06:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泰坦斯在賈米托夫·海曼手中創立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.35,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以其強大力量為背景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.17,0:06:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做比吉翁公國更壞的事業\N企圖統治人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令一方面,為了抵抗泰坦斯成立了奧古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.79,0:06:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前自護的紅色彗星夏亞·阿茲那布魯也參與其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.42,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類脫離地球控制的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未何人類還要爭戰不休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,污染地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.89,0:06:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許人永遠不可能覺醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前我們有阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我們有卡繆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.69,0:06:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這混沌的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,許多人們被巨大海浪吞沒\N熄滅生命之火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.73,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪奉命攻下格林普斯2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.74,0:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了治癒受傷的身心\N前往SIDE 1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往西航行0301
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.42,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我們打敗了西洛克 擊沉了朱庇特利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是代價也太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.59,0:07:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧古的指導者夏亞·阿茲那布魯沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡繆也情況不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身心都受到重創
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須早一些到達SIDE 1才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來在這裏,花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心卡繆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.44,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1有好醫生,提起精神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡繆，你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.39,0:08:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達，冠武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡繆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.45,0:08:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.94,0:08:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我們經常吵架\N你總是那麼溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要加入戰鬥的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊,花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是去看MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看自己的MS是哪一款吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎,\N你只是後補駕駛員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來支援的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你趁現在休息好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一場作戰很快就開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡繆，可是你的心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.07,0:09:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！你怎麼還要讓這種事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.22,0:09:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼意思？阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.69,0:09:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不趕快阻止他們倆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說那個叫做鳳的女孩的事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想讓同樣的悲劇再度上演嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡繆 卡繆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡繆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.91,0:09:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到剛才我都想不起卡繆你了,\N這是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為你討厭我了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.13,0:09:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我變了,當坐上精神力高達時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳？鳳，你能跑嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳…你…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰？是敵人對吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要殺死你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.83,0:10:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡繆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.82,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，打開駕駛艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡繆，是你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能再留在精神力高達的駕駛艙裏了\N快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.68,0:10:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧，卡繆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑裏德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！你覺悟吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.22,0:11:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.57,0:11:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉！！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.47,0:11:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人總是重複同樣的錯誤,\N真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.27,0:11:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳，睜開眼睛吧，騙人的吧\N這是騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睜開眼睛啊，鳳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.17,0:11:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間的淚水留不止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.33,0:11:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰火中消逝的人們的思念\N何時才能達成呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最新MS名錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.81,0:12:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個問題，這台MS是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百式！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古華多羅·巴吉納，百式出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.42,0:12:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,你還裝蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞，也就是說古華多羅上尉戰鬥經驗都很豐富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.96,0:12:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥力高的百式 是本系列代表性的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.95,0:12:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第2個問題？這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力奇·戴亞斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.46,0:12:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是奧古開發的高機動MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.06,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力奇.戴亞斯的力奇\N意思是指宇宙用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.60,0:13:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴亞斯是取自喜望鋒的發現者巴斯羅謬·戴亞斯的姓氏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以叫力奇·戴亞斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.87,0:13:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說取這個名字是古華多羅上尉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人說使用高達合金的力奇·戴亞斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是第2代MS的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是高達MK-Ⅱ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.30,0:13:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對,這是超級高達\N他裝上了G防衛號的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.16,0:13:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然高達MK-Ⅱ是泰坦斯秘密開發的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因古華多羅與卡繆的活躍而成為了奧古的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要變形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,0085的MS的最大特徵,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.05,0:13:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個變形MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.48,0:13:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像燕子一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.47,0:13:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸札上尉的漢布拉克\N是3機為一隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是羅沙美亞姐姐的獵犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機器人迷當中,\N有人認為這是最美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.56,0:14:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達MK-Ⅱ你的實力就只有這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,色子高達出現了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂講 這是精神力高達才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.67,0:14:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的體型巨大很讓人驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了，看我的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡碧尼擁有應用了精神系統的浮游炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.23,0:14:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是用腦波控制的小型光束炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.50,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，最棒的MS當然是百式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.13,0:14:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然是Z高達最厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我實在是個倒楣人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.60,0:14:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達加上卡繆·比丹的新人類能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.34,0:14:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確發揮超強的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝浪者形態也很帥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.39,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作這麼大，卡繆哥哥怎麼都不會眼花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.34,0:15:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,最後是大家等候已久的 MS謎題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請將登場的MS名字與型號輸入電子郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.84,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答對的人,可抽選招待到木星旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請寄到SIDE 6第23區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦,好啦,你們可別當真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到了SIDE 3的阿克西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.56,0:17:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是扎比家的正統繼承者\N米涅芭·扎比公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.72,0:17:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用扎比家被忘記的繼承者 米涅芭·扎比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且聲稱有復興吉翁公國的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.30,0:17:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,各部隊都準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令全體艦隊發動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,哈曼大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.59,0:17:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1方面的軍艦巴西馬斯號,\N出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.25,0:17:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1的香格里拉殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.99,0:17:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香格里拉是最舊的宇宙殖民地\N因受到多次戰火摧殘而荒廢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.31,0:17:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連自轉速度都控制失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.65,0:18:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個SIDE都是由40個左右的殖民衛星構成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.36,0:18:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個殖民地由1開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依序取了偏號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.26,0:18:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 1到SIDE 7的宇宙都市\N是以太陽與月球與地球引力的中力點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.17,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉格朗日點為中心\N劃出各自運轉的軌道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集尖端科技而建造的宇宙殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有許多維持宇宙生活的設備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.96,0:18:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及許多安全系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是動畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.39,0:18:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是動畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是動畫，是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是動畫，是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.11,0:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，我是捷度·阿西塔\N住在SIDE 1香格里拉殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界真難混
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不出外工作就活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就當起收破爛的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.40,0:19:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的工作是撿回MS的廢鐵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.05,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這工作很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.98,0:19:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,我有可愛的妹妹與\N重要的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.45,0:19:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子都是新人類\N表現給大人看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 隊長是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪來到香格里拉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.71,0:20:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是大賺一筆的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那上面有Z高達啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.26,0:20:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要偷到它\N我們就能告別這個殖民衛星了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，一下子就得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.86,0:20:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撿回這怪人是一連串錯誤的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他叫逸札對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人要靠膽量，把Z高達搶過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.94,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.27,0:20:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果哥哥可以改掉這無拘無束的性格就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.06,0:20:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,累死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.26,0:20:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔！給我賺一筆吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好… 好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看看\N她也是亞加瑪的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿嘿…不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.83,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是\N亞加瑪有更厲害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是卡繆·比丹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那感覺究竟是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.21,0:21:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是新人類嗎？\N世界上真的有新人類嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我們先把Z高達搶過來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他的以後再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.50,0:21:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是每個月都有買MS雜誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.15,0:21:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達什麼的我肯定能操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.99,0:21:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,你別忘恩負義，我是救你的人啊！\N這個混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.04,0:21:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我最討厭大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.55,0:21:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.17,0:21:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你技術太嫩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.93,0:22:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？結果失敗了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.66,0:22:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,我看不過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度和比查你們繼續這樣下去行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有怪東西接近了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.60,0:22:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪追上來了\N為什麼我也得被拖下水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.12,0:22:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是男子漢吧\N自己惹的禍自己收拾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！我要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.25,0:22:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人類要是害怕的話\N還能來駕駛Z高達嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.50,0:22:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.50,0:22:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.50,0:23:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
